edge: Initially, Inaaya mistakenly believes that RJ is her ex-boyfriend Babloo Ranawat.
Inaaya used to be in a relationship with Babloo Ranawat.
RJ claims that he does not know Inaaya, who accuses him of being her ex-boyfriend Babloo Ranawat.
Babloo was recruited by CBI officer Azaad Khan to help stop Laila's plans.
CBi officer Azaad Khan is trying to stop Laila's plans.
Babloo was initially a member of Laila's gang.
Inaaya is the sister of Laila.
The bank account of the ambulance driver's wife Hema was hacked and her money went missing due to Laila's app.
Laila designed an app that steals users' data and their bank accounts' money.
Due to guilt, Babloo rejoins CBI officer Azaad Khan.
RJ meets Hema and learns about her husband's suicide due to bank account hacking caused by Laila's app.
